<LP>
   PARAMOUNT COMMUNICATIONS Inc. (New York) -- Peter D. Nalle
was appointed president of the Professional Information
Group, a unit of Simon &amp; Schuster, the publishing arm of this
communications concern. He assumes responsibilities
previously held by Jonathan Newcomb, 43 years old, who
continues as an executive vice president of the parent. Mr.
Nalle, 42, previously was president and chief executive
officer of J.B. Lippincott, the health-care publishing unit
of Harper &amp; Row.
