   A Western official declined to comment.
   In the filing, Arcade said it may seek to buy more shares,
dispose of them or seek to elect one or more of its designees
to Western's board.
   Another Norwegian company, Viking Supply Ships AS, has
acquired a 10.68% stake in Western and is considering seeking
support from other shareholders for a special meeting to
replace Western's board.
